Subject: [PATCH] fix: harden macOS session transfer sockets

Shorten the transfer listener socket path so it fits macOS SUN_LEN limits, move it into a dedicated namespace, and cover rename/startup behavior with regression tests.

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
